lead_paragraph: Rafa Nadal boasted after his first-round U.S. Open match that he had a video recording of being the first player to hit a ball in practice under the new roof at Arthur Ashe Stadium.

headline.print_headline: Nadal Completes 'Roof' Double at U.S. Open
